Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.68,0:22:06.00,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便可以拭去你的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:12.06,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而讓你流淚的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:18.91,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻一定無法僅用這雙手來承受
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.43,0:22:24.07,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不見的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.62,0:22:29.22,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我們緊緊聯系在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.73,0:22:32.40,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用心去感受
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.51,0:22:36.31,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力深呼吸（深呼吸）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:42.10,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試著去深呼吸的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.70,0:22:46.05,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕是獨自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.36,0:22:49.05,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對無法跨越的屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.27,0:22:54.06,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 只要和你一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.39,0:22:59.93,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論什麼困難都能跨越
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.40,0:23:05.94,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能繼續努力下去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.56,0:00:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒冰魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.33,0:00:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話講在前頭 這可不是我的興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...我的背...背有點疼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.96,0:00:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我一直工作到天亮嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.65,0:00:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢 槍水學姐的腳看起來好像很舒服的樣子~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就拜託我說「幫忙踩一下」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.70,0:00:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.65,0:00:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 先隨便找個地方坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.60,0:00:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 工作是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.29,0:00:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我加入了輕小說研究會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要長時間坐在電腦前面所以就...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.79,0:00:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你有在寫小說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起來的話我是更喜歡遊戲之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.47,0:00:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.27,0:00:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還是連規則都不懂的「狗」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 在這圓桌旁坐下 學會戰斗的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能成為被稱為「狼」的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.67,0:00:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帥氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.67,0:00:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺悟不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就先...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.65,0:01:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐的...好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.53,0:01:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都行 反正趕緊給我簽上名字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.80,0:01:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是入社申請書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.53,0:01:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.48,0:01:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.45,0:01:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我「別在意」 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是旁邊有一位簽完名就不省人事的家伙在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.56,0:01:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 所以別管那家伙..你也要快點寫呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群笨蛋 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.69,0:01:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了半價便當而賭上性命 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.37,0:01:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真的好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.09,0:01:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白 什麼都不用說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.95,0:01:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入社申請書 確實已經收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同志們 歡迎加入半價同好會 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平成23年（2011年） 4月7日早上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.03,0:01:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又死了一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.50,0:02:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#02 味增煮青花魚便當 674kcal
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.46,0:03:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在貼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是西區的超市的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數字代表便當變成半價的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.13,0:03:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我個人推薦這兩處
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍克商場和常磐超市
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.68,0:03:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們知道霍克吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是昨晚你們在那戰斗過的那家超市
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說兩邊都很容易陷入激戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相應地 也是能讓你們得到教育的好地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這兩家超市都是我的地盤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我就暫時先到別的地方去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.54,0:04:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你們好運
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍克商場的半價神 油神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他貼完以前都不可以輕舉妄動是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.75,0:04:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰斗有幾條規則
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.19,0:04:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說 不能在半價神離開賣場前出手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 貼完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能在半價神離開賣場前出手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 佐藤同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:05:00.15,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}炸豬扒便當
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:04:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能獵取超過當晚自己吃的分量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.92,0:05:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 這就是「狼」的戰斗方式嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.78,0:05:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有著各種各樣的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是全部都能歸結於這一句話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.43,0:05:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵守禮儀 賭上尊嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.69,0:05:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去下一家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腰好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.02,0:05:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 小狗們 今天過來這邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 就是「狗」的意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 光頭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.67,0:05:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你又...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:05:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 沒事 事實上就是這樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 老頭要出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.10,0:06:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這家超市的半價神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半價神也有老爺爺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.58,0:06:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦克 是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要大地震了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.09,0:06:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.26,0:06:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等老頭把半價貼紙貼完大概還要5分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絡腮胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 在我們的狩獵場可不能讓那家伙亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是「大野豬」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,規則不起作用麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.70,0:06:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊 小狗們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:06:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 你們快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.97,0:07:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光靠你們是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶發女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒貼上半價貼紙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.68,0:07:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是全部哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 店員先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.43,0:07:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快貼上貼紙啊 貼紙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.76,0:07:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.49,0:07:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都是要貼 你就貼快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.67,0:07:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是「豬」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.04,0:07:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知羞恥 卻帶著能橫掃「狼」的獠牙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.36,0:07:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是「野豬」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.76,0:07:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都因為我們不夠成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.36,0:07:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都想讓老頭幸福地結束一天的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮儀和尊嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.48,0:07:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是去買那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:08:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 昨天是這麼一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...雖然是我碰過的 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.94,0:08:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.66,0:08:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然飯團還是要吃鮭魚的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.25,0:08:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 這邊也...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便當雖然也很好吃 不過這個也不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 還是很想吃便當啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 雖然有點不甘心 不過沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是名副其實的「大野豬」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.36,0:09:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是時候該講清楚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心裏是怎麼想白粉同學的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼又是這種像是要和情敵做個了斷的臺詞？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白粉同學是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有在聽嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.27,0:10:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...我想確認一下 這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是字面意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.27,0:10:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼想的才會讓她去爭奪半價便當這種東西呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.57,0:10:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是我強制她的 她是自己決定...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她才不會積極地去幹這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.37,0:10:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說 她實際上也這麼做了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以生氣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.37,0:10:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是 你想說白粉同學認為
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其跟我在一起 跟佐藤你在一起更好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.07,0:10:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也沒這樣說...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以踢你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.30,0:10:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會放棄 也不會認輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.39,0:10:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白梅梅.. baibai
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再胡扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.79,0:10:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白粉她今天不過來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 剛才...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,u u u...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:01.67,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}梅在日語裏面讀做ume
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說小梅 小梅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的 那個...是我小學以來唯一的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一定是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.49,0:11:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我寫的小說她也說很有趣 對我也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 當然不是指男歡女愛方面的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.90,0:11:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 為什麼提起小梅？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才對我又是打巴掌又是踢的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...就這樣被帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.93,0:11:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？ 要等下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.77,0:11:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11連敗 學姐你太強了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:11:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多是時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:11:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.41,0:12:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能成為「狼」就看你自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「狼」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:19.65,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}無標題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:19.65,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}今天的小梅很溫柔 但總覺得有點可怕... ..·.（>_<）.·..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是哪邊啊 看來又要惹白梅生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「風暴」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.86,0:12:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「風暴」？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.68,0:12:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了迎接春天的比賽而開始進行練習的橄欖球社
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這群家伙要是來了的話 便當和素材就會全被他們搶光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是所謂的天才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天才？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.90,0:12:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去另一家店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別勉強 別勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:12:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「風暴」再加上「大野豬」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄吧 放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...那個人是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.20,0:13:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[魔導士]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.25,0:13:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[魔導士] 是「狼」嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.91,0:13:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這下真不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連魔導士都來了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.13,0:13:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.84,0:13:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...我在這裡買丼兵衛算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「大野豬」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.18,0:13:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「風暴」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.95,0:13:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.67,0:13:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[魔導士]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:14:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...你是說別買烏冬面 買蕎麥面嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是想要成為「狼」嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要嘗過一次血的味道 就再也變不回單純的「狗」了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后也會忍受不了「豬」的屈辱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.73,0:14:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵守禮儀 賭上尊嚴 對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再讓你往前一步的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在老頭貼完貼紙以前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點 再撐一會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 老頭大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔導士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.23,0:15:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正中下懷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用對手的勢頭 再順勢避開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來已經結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 是「暴風」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.09,0:15:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便當和素材 全都給我帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？難道說這家伙是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.91,0:15:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[魔導士]！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 蠢豬們 今晚可沒有飼料喂你們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.34,0:16:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 不愧是[魔導士]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絡腮胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.77,0:16:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶發女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.11,0:16:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[狼]..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.63,0:16:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能讓你們搶盡風頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.67,0:16:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「豬」才不配吃半價便當
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.85,0:16:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.12,0:16:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跟這群狼糾纏 去搶便當！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月桂冠..就算拼了命也不能把月桂冠讓給他們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月桂冠？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:42.41,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}月桂冠：半價便當中被半價神貼上特別貼紙的便當。視每家店不同貼上各自的貼紙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這群蠢豬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.26,0:16:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知羞恥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.89,0:16:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是目的還是禮儀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是尊嚴還是其他一切都忘掉了的一群蠢豬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱就該揍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:16:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豬就該宰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:16:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.81,0:17:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘了身為「狼」的矜持 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為「狼」的矜持？ 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書包忘在社團活動室了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白粉同學很消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是因為佐藤和學姐的關系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝傻嗎？我要生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天你就做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵件？是白粉發過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:15.79,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}學姐和佐藤同學都沒有給我回復
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:15.79,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}是不是因為我寫的郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:15.79,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}很煩人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:15.79,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}很惡心？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:15.79,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}如果是的話 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.21,0:18:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是的話 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.42,0:18:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的 是因為白梅她會生氣...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:26.60,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}寫郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:26.60,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}To：白粉花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:26.60,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}RE:對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:27.11,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}有來電
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:27.11,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}未知號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人了 你是惡意騷擾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以讓我把你的手機變成廢鐵嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這樣做了對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.52,0:18:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.03,0:18:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 有了 有了 書包
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛接到了一個相當繞圈子的像是殺人預告的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.74,0:18:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白粉她現在是什麼情況？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.09,0:18:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白梅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 難道說你在等我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？算是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說昨天也是在這裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次勝利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聞起來不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.24,0:19:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味增煮青花魚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道這是什麼東西才拿的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.75,0:19:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個便當上貼的是月桂冠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.71,0:19:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月桂冠？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.95,0:19:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是半價神在剩下的便當裏面挑出最有自信的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再在上面貼上的特別的貼紙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在存在著月桂冠的領域裏的人都會以這個為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當天得到這個的人會成為該領域裏面絕對的勝利者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.94,0:19:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.32,0:19:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次勝利就拿到月桂冠 說不定你能成大器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.53,0:19:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧 畢竟對手是「暴風」嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:20:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 被稱為[魔導士]的「狼」有過來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[魔導士]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.63,0:20:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是這學校的三年級生 叫金城優
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.03,0:20:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就先記住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.36,0:20:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金城優？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.05,0:20:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 有這麼多月桂冠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.70,0:20:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一張都裝滿了回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.79,0:20:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再慢慢說給你聽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.28,0:20:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 自己親手貼上去吧 佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要寫上日期和名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.93,0:20:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.78,0:20:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 細細品嘗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.29,0:21:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.79,0:21:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先等下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要先說「我開動了」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.82,0:21:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對把它做出來的人 把它變成半價的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.89,0:21:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及成為了食材的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs48}還有對那些同樣很想得到手卻被你奪走了的人們的敬意和感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.53,0:21:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.87,0:21:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.09,0:23:16.34,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}梅的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集我也會從佐藤手中繼續保護白粉同學 敬請期待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.88,0:23:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？說多一點？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.27,0:23:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要我再說點什麼？吵醒了白粉同學怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.77,0:23:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要扁你了哦
